api

Class RequestManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.RequestManager

  • public class RequestManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which handles making API transactions to outside sources. This class is implemented as Singleton to ensure that requests are made in a synchronous fashion, thus negating any concerns about some requests externally processing faster than others which may cause errors depending on the cloud APIs which are used.
